{"tid":842042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵】讚國家多方面成就輝煌　張建宗：我們身為中國人非常自豪","createTime":"2018-09-30T03:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T08:39:05.000Z","uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"814a316e9d26ef15ab6412330dca1e1582aa7558","tid":842042,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"耗資逾844億元的高鐵香港段上周日終於通車，政務司長張建宗今早發表網誌指，通車標誌着香港昂然邁進「高鐵時代」新征程，又說國家在多方面取得輝煌成就，「我們身為中國人感到非常自豪」。<br />\n<br />\n網誌題為＜邁進新時代 展開新征程＞，張建宗先預告明天是「中華人民共和國成立六十九周年的大日子」，適逢國家推行改革開放政策40周年，意義重大，「在這個高興的大日子，我衷心祝願祖國富強昌盛，國泰民安，香港繁榮穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗之後談及高鐵，形容高鐵香港段通車「標誌着香港昂然邁進『高鐵時代』的新征程」，將香港連接至內地各大城市，進一步增強協同效應，創造「無限發展機遇」。他又說，過去40年國家發展一日千里，在國際政治、經濟、科技等領域有舉足輕重地位，稱「國家在多方面取得輝煌成就，我們身為中國人感到非常自豪」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗最後強調：「我們需要不斷壯大實力，力求進步，與時俱進，才能穩坐國家發展的『快車』，全速向前邁進。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180930/s00001/1538267269190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180930%2Fs00001%2F1538267269190&d=VgDisFYbR%2F7l5trZ3dsCHI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1e429a25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180930%2Fs00001%2F1538267269190&h=c8ff9dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180930/s00001/1538267269190</a><br />\n<br />\n有無野想同光頭佬講？？<br />\n<br />\n我們？？邊個我們？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6fd10c67ee6bf4a836fce5570d6e7fd7fb1fd6","tid":842042,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"點解咁多光頭佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e645ec85c933badd5d192ed6c874078129d5447","tid":842042,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:02:50.000Z","msg":"咁快d制裁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62449aecb0f7adb955e9ac0061767def55da551","tid":842042,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好慘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想個天俾返啲頭髮光頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2668c8c56f3f55f8417e3f80d5701cf2609c61a1","tid":842042,"uid":44105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"肥平未出事之前都係咁講<br />\n出左事, 嬴國有無出過一句聲救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfaddddb66581dcbbf8896fefa5ddc5671d2074","tid":842042,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2668c8c56f3f55f8417e3f80d5701cf2609c61a1","tid":842042,"uid":44105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"肥平未出事之前都係咁講<br />\n出左事, 嬴國有無出過一句聲救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"狆蟈口交部稱要求美方徹查事件真相，嚴懲肇事者，以及時向狆方通報情況。狆方要求妥善處理此事，維護當事人合法權益。"},{"pid":"2a654a6d428e8ae58e8c2bab54ed89311238089a","tid":842042,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike